21.title: Table of contents
21.content: . We considered multiple numerical attributes that could descried how different input data could influence strength of PathFX predictions. We were particularly interested in how side-effect-associated genes in drug networks (“neighborhood gene lists”) and how side-effect pathway genes (“interactome gene lists”) changed. We pursued multiple metrics that quantified changes in neighborhood and interactome gene lists (Table X). Table X. Numerical attribute quantified changes in underlying PathFX data – specifically changes in neighborhood and interactome gene lists and relationships between these data.
